parameters:
[Manager] If you're going to work here and go places, you'll need to be
able to move around freely.
[Manager] I think if you're as cute as Anna-chan, you can earn a lot...
[Manager] It's not good to let loose too much, okay? â™¥
[Anastasia] I can't believe there's a place like this in this town...

[Manager] Well, for girls, it's a place that only those who work here
have any connection to, so it's not surprising that you don't know
about it.

[Manager] And besides, this place is run by the lord of this town. It
seems they're making a lot of money by inviting quite a high-ranking
nobles... If we were to talk about it openly, it wouldn't end well.

[Manager] I've heard that only the important people from the Academy...
are against this place.

[Anastasia] (There might be some connection between my father's
downfall and this place...)

[Anastasia] (The lord of this town... judging by the timing, there must
be some connection between the principal, that woman, and him...)

[Anastasia] (Since I unexpectedly came to this place... I'll also try
to search for clues that connect to the lord.)
